OL,7,FSouthern Water has issued an apology
OL,8,Fafter confirming that some customers'
OL,9,Fpersonal data has been stolen in an
OL,10,Fillegal cyber attack on the company.
OL,12,FThe firm, which has its headquarters
OL,13,Fin Worthing, West Sussex says the data
OL,14,Fstolen could include customers' names,
OL,15,Fdates of births, national insurance
OL,16,Fnumbers, and bank details including
OL,17,Fsort codes and bank account numbers.
