OL,7,FAn investigation was launched on 22
OL,8,FJanuary (2024) when the utilities firm
OL,9,Fbecame aware that a cyber criminal
OL,10,Forganisation was claiming on its
OL,11,Fwebsite to have stolen data from some
OL,12,Fof our IT systems.
OL,14,FSouthern Water is reassuring customers
OL,15,Fthat operations and services have not
OL,16,Fbeen impacted and water supply is
OL,17,Funaffected.
